            div
                span.redText Rules:
            span.normalText 1. Memes only! Posts other than memes will be deleted and may result in a ban!
            br
            br
            span.normalText 2. Memes that are considered too SPICY or inappropriate may be subject to deletion.
            br
            br
            span.normalText 3. Farming likes with fake accounts will lead to the boot!
            br
            br
            span.normalText 4. If your meme is so bad it never gets a like, you will be terminated by the meme king!
